      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a great new home for it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
