      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that delivers a linear power band up to a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis has been meticulously preserved, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a documented rod bearing replacement to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gates, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The exterior retains its factory-depth luster with zero oxidation, while the interior leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A definitive turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak BMW M-division dynamics.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
