    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that can only be described as a time capsule. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in absolute showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original factory scent lingers. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a chassis that has never seen inclement weather, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
